  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large pot over medium heat and add the softened butter.",
    "Saut\u00e9 the diced onion and minced garlic until fragrant and translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the diced yaut\u00eda and stir to coat with the butter and aromatics.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and low\u2011fat milk, bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Reduce heat to a simmer and cook, uncovered, until the yaut\u00eda is tender, about 15 minutes.",
    "Use an immersion blender to puree the soup until silky smooth; if desired, blend in batches.",
    "Season with salt, pepper, and a splash of lemon juice; stir to combine.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot."
